//History

The bootstrap was developed by mark Otto and jacob thornton.
It is an open source product on git hub.


//container

Using container for giving space in the webpage.(use .container)
Using container well for giving border for that sentence in the webpage.(use .container well)
Using container-fluid well for giving border for full webpage.(use .container-fluid well)

//Grid System


lg-Larger device
md-Medium device
sm-smaller device
xs-Extra smaller device

.col-md-2-->col-column
            md-medium device
            2-column size
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-2 well">box1</div>
    <div class="col-md-2 well">box2</div>
    <div class="col-md-2 well">box3</div>
    <div class="col-md-2 well">box4</div>
    <div class="col-md-2 well">box5</div>
    <div class="col-md-2 well">box6</div>

//Text Property
 *we give text color in the paragraph using (class="text-primary")
 *we give background color in the paragraph using (class="bg-primary")
 *lead it is used for highlight a word.(class="lead")
 *small is used for reduce the size of the word.(class="small")
 *alignment-text alignment for webpage.(class="text-justify")
   text-right
   text-left
   text-center
   text-justify
*font
    text-uppercase
    text-lowercase
    text-capitalize


//Table Format
   *table-striped--->It give zebra color in the table
   *table-bordered--->It give border for a table
   *table-condensed--->It remove padding in the table
   *table-hover--->It shows arrow mark in the table with blink
   *table-responsive--->It uses in div class and it is for using in the mobile phone.

   <body>
    <div class="responsive">
<table class=" table table-striped">
    <tr>
        <th>S.no</th>
        <th>Name</th>
        <th>contact</th>
        <th>email</th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <th>1.</th>
        <th>Arun</th>
        <th>12345</th>
        <th>arun.com</th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <th>2.</th>
        <th>Varun</th>
        <th>1234578</th>
        <th>varun.com</th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <th>3.</th>
